t</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel-cell"><div class="slide-inner pix-p-20"><div class="pix-slider-effects"><div class="card"><div class="pix-content-box card        white rounded-lg shadow-sm scale-sm bg-light-opacity-1 w-100  "><div class="" style="z-index:30;position:relative;"><div class="card pix-p-10 rounded-lg"><div class="card-body"><p class="card-text font-italic text-white ">Une &eacute;quipe professionnelle, chaleureuse, redoutablement efficace. S'ils n'avaient pas &eacute;t&eacute; &agrave; nos cot&eacute;s nous aurions abandonner ce projet Un grand merci et bravo</p><div class="d-flex"><div class="align-self-center"><h6 class="card-title mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-white">BRICO RELAIS</h6><div class="card-title  mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-primary">G&eacute;rante</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel-cell"><div class="slide-inner pix-p-20"><div class="pix-slider-effects"><div class="card"><div class="pix-content-box card        white rounded-lg shadow-sm scale-sm bg-light-opacity-1 w-100  "><div class="" style="z-index:30;position:relative;"><div class="card pix-p-10 rounded-lg"><div class="card-body"><p class="card-text font-italic text-white ">Agence r&eacute;active et disponible, &agrave; l'&eacute;coute de nos besoins et en appui pour nous conseiller au mieux ! Un tr&egrave;s beau site bient&ocirc;t en ligne, qui, je suis s&ucirc;re contribuera au d&eacute;veloppement de notre activit&eacute; ! Merci &agrave; l'&eacute;quipe Orbiteo &#128521;</p><div class="d-flex"><div class="align-self-center"><h6 class="card-title mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-white">PERTINENCE RH</h6><div class="card-title  mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-primary">Conseill&egrave;re RH</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel-cell"><div class="slide-inner pix-p-20"><div class="pix-slider-effects"><div class="card"><div class="pix-content-box card        white rounded-lg shadow-sm scale-sm bg-light-opacity-1 w-100  "><div class="" style="z-index:30;position:relative;"><div class="card pix-p-10 rounded-lg"><div class="card-body"><p class="card-text font-italic text-white ">Merci &agrave; Adrien et son &eacute;quipe  pour la cr&eacute;ation de notre site Internet. Merci &eacute;galement &agrave; Yannick  pour sa r&eacute;activit&eacute;  son efficacit&eacute; et sa sympathie.  Nous vous souhaitons plein de belles choses dans l'avenir du digital. On ne regrette pas de vous avoir fait confiance  pour notre projet.</p><div class="d-flex"><div class="align-self-center"><h6 class="card-title mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-white">AS TRAITEUR</h6><div class="card-title  mb-0 pix-mx-20 font-weight-bold text-primary">Charg&eacute;e de Marketing</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="el1625728410874-d54541da-6f59" class="w-100 d-block "></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row-full-width vc_clearfix"></div><section data-vc-full-width="true" data-vc-full-width-init="false" class="vc_section vc_section_visible pix-intro-1 vc_custom_1626007827696 vc_section-has-fill" data-section-name=""><div class="fullpage-container"><div class="pix-intro-img jarallax" data-jarallax data-speed="0.8"><img class="jarallax-img pix-opacity-10 ewww_webp_lazy_load" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="ORBITEO, ORBITEO Bonjour !" data-lazy-src="https://orbiteo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/5.jpg" data-lazy-src-webp="https://orbiteo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/5.jpg.webp"><noscript><img loading="lazy" class="jarallax-img pix-opacity-10" src="https://orbiteo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/5.jpg" alt="ORBITEO, ORBITEO Bonjour !"></noscript></div></div><div data-vc-full-width="true" data-vc-full-width-init="false" class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row_visible"><div c